Material: GOLD; JASPER; AGATE; TURQUOISE; SERPENTINITE; MALACHITE; CARNELIAN; AMETHYST
Name: Necklace with amulets
Description: The necklace consists of beads of all shapes and sizes of turquoise, serpentine, malachite, carnelian, amethyst, bandachite and gold, with many amulets and pendants of gold, jasper, serpentine and agate. The central piece is made of embossed gold plaques. One udjat-eye is flanked by two uraei.
